# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# CONVEX CONFIGURATION (Required)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Your Convex deployment URL
# 
# How to get this:
#   Option 1: Run 'bunx convex dev' and follow the prompts
#   Option 2: Go to https://dashboard.convex.dev → Your Project → Settings
#
# Example: https://happy-animal-123.convex.cloud
PUBLIC_CONVEX_URL=

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# CONVEX DEPLOY KEY (Optional - for production/CI)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Only needed for production deployments or CI/CD pipelines
#
# How to get this:
#   Go to https://dashboard.convex.dev → Your Project → Settings → Deploy Keys
#
# Example: prod:abc123xyz...
# CONVEX_DEPLOY_KEY=

